item.title: About
item.description: I’m Jaan, a self taught programmer. At the moment I’m trying to get into app development by learning native Android. After years of aimlessly learning random programming languages for fun, now I’m trying to commit to one and make useful programs. I started coding after graduating high school, after I got curious about Linux from the show Mr. Robot. The first months, I’ve probably distro-hopped more than my fingers could count, using my neighbor’s WiFi to download ISOs (sorry!
